; Coverage test for account.cc lookup switch cases.
; Exercises the 'h' case (L442-445, has_children_to_display),
; 'n' case (L467-472, note), 'N' case (L496-499), 'O' case (L501-504),
; 'e' case (L435-440, earliest), and other lookup branches.

2024/01/01 Grocery
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Gas Station
    Expenses:Gas     $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --format "%(has_children_to_display ? 'Y' : 'N') %(account)\n"
N Assets:Cash
Y Expenses
N Expenses:Food
N Expenses:Gas
Y 
end test
